text: Giorgini is an Italian surname. Notable people with the surname include: *Aldo Giorgini (1934–1994), Italian artist *Daniele Giorgini (born 1984), Italian tennis player *Frank Giorgini, American ceramist *Mass Giorgini (born 1968), American musician and record producer *Saskia Giorgini, Italian-Dutch pianist ==See also== *6775 Giorgini, a main-belt asteroid Category:Italian-language surnames
